565
00:42:09,990 --> 00:42:13,250
There was a situation today.

566
00:42:15,370 --> 00:42:17,930
What's all this?

567
00:42:17,930 --> 00:42:19,170
This?

568
00:42:19,170 --> 00:42:22,410
