592
00:44:21,430 --> 00:44:28,100
Dan Dan. Don't assume about your brother so easily and be quick to speak ill of him.

593
00:44:28,100 --> 00:44:30,700
Dae Beom is not the kind of person to go around and make trouble.

594
00:44:30,700 --> 00:44:37,130
