597
00:44:45,590 --> 00:44:48,430
You go first, Dad.

598
00:44:48,430 --> 00:44:50,910
Okay.

599
00:45:05,470 --> 00:45:08,830
This is a super expensive brand.

600
00:45:08,830 --> 00:45:12,540
Where did he get the money to buy this?

601
00:45:22,940 --> 00:45:24,860
Hi.

602
00:45:26,730 --> 00:45:29,050
How have you been?

603
00:45:29,050 --> 00:45:33,910
Jin Sang Goo... Why are you here?

604
00:45:33,910 --> 00:45:36,060
You recognized me even though it's been a while.

605
00:45:36,060 --> 00:45:39,230
Well, you should recognize your husband.

606
00:45:39,230 --> 00:45:43,010
How dare you come here? Get the hell out of here.

607
00:45:43,010 --> 00:45:46,600
I don't want to look at you even for a second.

608
00:45:46,600 --> 00:45:49,100
