655
00:49:18,940 --> 00:49:22,350
Se Chan came home two hours late,

656
00:49:22,350 --> 00:49:25,420
but he told me he was going to a friend's birthday party beforehand.

657
00:49:25,420 --> 00:49:32,850
Se Jong ate his food without being picky at home and also at the kindergarten.

