661
00:49:52,820 --> 00:49:55,800
I'm very sorry.

662
00:50:01,810 --> 00:50:03,460
Okay.

663
00:50:03,460 --> 00:50:07,120
But if you can, I'd rather him not eat junk food.

664
00:50:07,120 --> 00:50:10,800
If he eats it again, please let me know in advance.

665
00:50:10,800 --> 00:50:12,590
Okay.

666
00:50:12,590 --> 00:50:15,110
Good night.

667
00:50:16,880 --> 00:50:20,120
Good night to you too.

668
00:50:27,900 --> 00:50:33,100
