670
00:51:27,970 --> 00:51:30,460
[Baby Box]

671
00:52:17,160 --> 00:52:19,230
Mom.

672
00:52:19,230 --> 00:52:23,260
Sarah. Was it then?

673
00:52:27,260 --> 00:52:30,070
What are you talking about in the middle of the night?

674
00:52:30,070 --> 00:52:32,060
I'm going to sleep. Get out.

675
00:52:32,060 --> 00:52:34,850
Six years ago...

676
00:52:34,850 --> 00:52:38,500
You told me...

677
00:52:38,500 --> 00:52:43,570
You told me that you're going on a trip.

678
00:52:43,570 --> 00:52:47,160
And you were gone for half a year.

679
00:52:47,160 --> 00:52:49,530
Was it then?

680
00:52:49,530 --> 00:52:55,080
Did you give birth, all alone?

681
00:52:56,590 --> 00:53:01,250
Tell me... Tell me the truth!

682
00:53:01,250 --> 00:53:04,100
What did you do to the baby?

683
00:53:04,120 --> 00:53:05,920
Did you abandon him?

684
00:53:05,920 --> 00:53:08,470
