685
00:53:08,490 --> 00:53:13,190
Mom, really! What baby?

686
00:53:13,190 --> 00:53:16,420
No. It's not true!

687
00:53:16,420 --> 00:53:21,700
Why are you doing this?! Get out!

688
00:53:21,700 --> 00:53:25,060
In the past, I...

689
00:53:25,060 --> 00:53:28,720
I saw you clutching onto a baby blanket...

690
00:53:28,720 --> 00:53:33,420
