691
00:53:33,420 --> 00:53:37,160
That's not something a young lady would do!

692
00:53:37,160 --> 00:53:39,480
Where is that baby blanket?

693
00:53:39,480 --> 00:53:41,630
Where is it? What did you do with it!

694
00:53:41,630 --> 00:53:44,560
