725
00:56:30,720 --> 00:56:33,160
So...

726
00:56:33,180 --> 00:56:40,790
So, that's why you were so devoted to the Chairman Lee..?

727
00:56:40,790 --> 00:56:43,760
Because of Se Jong?

728
00:56:43,760 --> 00:56:48,270
