731
00:57:09,730 --> 00:57:11,840
What are you saying?

732
00:57:11,840 --> 00:57:14,800
Se Jong's grandmother took him?

733
00:57:14,800 --> 00:57:18,530
Yes. Se Jong called her grandma, so...

