755
00:58:35,270 --> 00:58:37,880
Just one minute!

756
00:58:41,060 --> 00:58:42,170
Mom.

757
00:58:42,170 --> 00:58:47,990
Hey, Sarah! I'm with Se Jong right now!

758
00:58:47,990 --> 00:58:54,350
That's why I want you to come here too. This place is...

759
00:58:56,220 --> 00:59:00,420
Alright. Alright.

760
00:59:00,420 --> 00:59:04,430
My goodness...

761
00:59:04,430 --> 00:59:10,080
Ms. Park, it's me. Don't worry about Se Jong.

762
00:59:10,080 --> 00:59:12,650
Really?

763
00:59:12,650 --> 00:59:17,920
